	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pergratas tuas heri literas accepi, S. D. ac summas gratias ago tibi de tuis novis, quas a <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822">Germania</placeName> accepisti, tum maxime de his, que in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2721">Panonia</placeName> accijderunt.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed illud est mihi novum creditu, quod non sit mortuus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18593">Solimanus</persName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2510">Turcharum</placeName> imperator, nempe ultra quod illud a duobus vel tribus locis ex <placeName ref="l822" type="citizen_name">Germania</placeName> accepi, adhuc nuper ex literis maiestatis regine nostre mihi est confirmatum, ac quod cum summo applausu sit receptus ad imperium <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18593">Selimus</persName> <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p21130">filius</persName>.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed ut ego suspicor, est maxima consuetudo <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822">Germanorum</placeName> nugas dicere, maxime vero illi, qui partes <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875">Hispanicas</placeName> fovent, ita id, quod cogitaverint, velint illud ita fieri.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De transitu regis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875">Hispaniae</placeName> per <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l648">Rhetos</placeName> vel pro copiis mittendis adversus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l640">Flandros</placeName> per illam viam, quod sit illi iter brevior, si dominus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8160">Bellenerius</persName>, predecessor meus, impedivit conatus suorum in illis partibus et passum, ego certissime ardentius et cum maiori animo illud faciam, quoniam adhuc, quod nunquam ex genio meo amaverim <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875">Hispanos</placeName>, probe scio illud non esse ex re maiestatis domini regis mei.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Qui, si ita mihi loqui fas erit, emit illum passum, neque mihi exprobrabitur, quod diligentiam non solum adhibeam in illa re, sed in aliis, que damnum semper adferent simili inimico domini Iesu Christi, dabo operam totis viribus dare impedimentum.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De literis tuis dedi operam hodie, ut cito et secure perferantur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Bene vale in domino, et bene sit tibi et familie.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l144">Erlibach</placeName> 20. novembre.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Amicissimus in omnibus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p931">P[ierre] de Grantrye</persName>.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Dem eerwürdigenn unnd wolgelerten meyster <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name">Heinrychen Bullinger</persName>, dienner der kilchen <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Zürich</placeName>, sinem günstigen herren.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Zürych</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
